commits.content:
{
    "security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles": "open",
    "editor.autoClosingBrackets": "never",
    "editor.autoClosingDelete": "never",
    "editor.autoClosingOvertype": "never",
    "editor.autoClosingQuotes": "never",
    "editor.accessibilitySupport": "off",
    "editor.autoSurround": "never",
    "javascript.suggest.includeAutomaticOptionalChainCompletions": false,
    "javascript.suggest.enabled": false,
    "javascript.suggest.autoImports": false,
    "javascript.suggest.includeCompletionsForImportStatements": false,
    "typescript.autoClosingTags": false,
    "typescript.check.npmIsInstalled": false,
    "javascript.updateImportsOnFileMove.enabled": "always",
    "javascript.autoClosingTags": false,
    "html.autoClosingTags": false,
    "less.completion.triggerPropertyValueCompletion": false,
    "scss.completion.triggerPropertyValueCompletion": false,
    "less.completion.completePropertyWithSemicolon": false,
    "scss.completion.completePropertyWithSemicolon": false,
    "editor.acceptSuggestionOnEnter": "off",
    "editor.fontFamily": "Consolas, 'Malgun Gothic', 'monospace'",
    "diffEditor.wordWrap": "off",
    "editor.wordWrap": "on",
    "editor.detectIndentation": false,
    "workbench.editorAssociations": {
        "*.json": "default"
    },
    "typescript.updateImportsOnFileMove.enabled": "always",
    "window.zoomLevel": 1,
    "eslint.alwaysShowStatus": true,
    "eslint.workingDirectories": ["./apps"],
    
}
